Package org.example.project_wobimich.dto

Klasse RealTimeMonitorDTO

java.lang.Object
org.example.project_wobimich.dto.RealTimeMonitorDTO
public class RealTimeMonitorDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object for real-time transport line monitoring.

Stores information about a public transport line such as line ID, line name, direction, type of transportation, accessibility, real-time support and upcoming departure times.
